quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  4,36,"Rewee Alla wata on kafidu e Makko hay huunde. JibimЙ“e on Й“en moЖҙЖҙoЙ—on e maЙ“Й“e, e joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral'en, e wonduЙ“e Й“en, e waasuЙ“e Й“en, e kawtaljo jom-Й“adondiral, e kawtal baЕӢЕӢe, e wonndiЙ—Й—o baЕӢЕӢe, e Й“ii laawol, e Й“en Й“e jeyruЙ—on Гұaame mon. Pellet, Alla YiЙ—aa kala on laatiiЙ—o ГұaaЖҙoowo mantotooЙ—o"
  4,37,"ЖҒen Й“e no wudda, Й“e yamira yimЙ“e Й“en nguddam, Й“e suuЙ—a kon ko Alla okki Й“e e ЖҒural Makko. Men Maranii heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte hoynooje"
  4,38,"E Й“en Й“e no nafqira jawle mun Й—en ka yiinorgol yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“e gomЙ—iЕӢtaa Alla wanaa Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden. Kala on mo seytaane wonani Й—um ciЕӢkotaaЙ—o : haray o bonii ciЕӢkodaaЙ—o"
  4,39,E ko honЙ—um fawinoo Й“e si Й“e gomЙ—inno Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden Й“e nafqi e kon ko Alla Arsike Й“e ? Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o Й“e
  4,40,"Pellet, Alla TooГұirtaa yeru jarra-hun, si wonii ko moЖҙЖҙere, O Soway nde, O Okka immorde ka Mokko njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,41,"Ko honno si tawii Men Addoyii immorde e kala mofte seeditotooЙ—o, Men Adde e dow Й“ee Й—oo ko a seeditotooЙ—o"
  4,42,"Nden Г‘alnde, heeferЙ“e Й“n e yedduЙ“e Й“en NulaaЙ—o on yeloto hara nun Й“e fonndeteno e leydi ndin, Й“e suuЙ—ataa Alla yeewtere"
  4,43,"Ko onon yo gimЙ—imЙ“e, wata on Й“aЙ—to julde den hara ko on siwruЙ“e haa anndon ko wowloton ; wanaa ka modduЙ—on e lonngal, si wanaa hara ko on taЖҙitooЙ“e laawol haa laЙ“Й“inoЙ—on. Si on laatike nawnuЙ“e, maa hiЙ—on e hoore jahal, maa Й“aawo hoggo arii goЙ—Й—o e mon(yaadon dow wuro), maa on soccondirii e rewЙ“e Й“en on heЙ“aali ndiyam, taamoree mbullaari(leydi) laaЙ“undi : mowlon geece mon Й—en e juuЙ—e mon Й—en. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo Yawtanoowo"
  4,44,"E a yi'aali faade e Й“en okkaaЙ“e geЙ“al e Й—efte Й—en, hiЙ“e sooda majjere nden, hiЙ“e faalaa nde majjoton laawol [foccondirngol] ngol"
  4,45,"Ko Alla ЖҒuri Anndude ayЙ“e mon Й“en. Alla yonii GiЙ—o, Alla yonii Ballo"
  4,46,"Hino e Й“eya alyahuudaaЙ“e waylooЙ“e konngol ngol e nokku maggol Й“e wi'a: \"Men nanii men yeddii ; heЙ—o ko wanaa nannateeЙ—o, aynu men\", ka hallugol Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en e yuwugol ka diina. Hara nun Й“e wi'ayno : \"Men nanii men Й—oftike nanu ndaaraa\", ko Й—um Й“uraynoo moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e, Й“ura foccaade. Ko woni tun, Alla HuЙ—irii Й“e geddi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й“e gomЙ—iЕӢtaa si wanaa seeЙ—aa"
  4,47,"Ko onon yo Й“eya okkanooЙ“e Defte, gomЙ—inee nden nde Men Jippini googinnde Й—en wonЙ—e ka mon, ado Men Mehude geece [mon Й—en] Men RuttiraЙ—e Й“abbe majje, maa Men HuЙ—ira Й“e wano Men HuЙ—irnoo non yimЙ“e asewe Й“en. Fiyaake Alla on Laatke LaatiЕӢteeЙ—um"
  4,48,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa kafidoowo Mo e goЙ—Й—um, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi Й—um wonannde on Mo O Muuyi. Kala on kafiduЙ—o Alla e goЙ—Й—um, gomЙ—ii o fepandiima bakkaatu mawЙ—o"
  4,49,"E a yi'aali Й“en Й“e no laЙ“Й“ina pittaali maЙ“Й“e ? Ko woni, Ko Alla LaЙ“Й“iЕӢta on Mo O Muuyi, Й“e tooГұoytaake yeru gurun tamaro"
  4,50,Ndaarii ko hol no Й“e woni fefindoraade e Alla fenaade ! ЖҠum Й—on yonii bakkaatu feeГұuЙ—o
  4,51,"E a yi'aali faade e Й“en okkanooЙ“e geЙ“al ka Deftere, hiЙ“e gomЙ—ina ndaaro e bewinayЙ—i Й—in, hiЙ“e wi'ana Й“en heeferЙ“e : \"Ko Й“ee Й—oo Й“uri feewude laawol e dii Й“eya gomЙ—ime"
  4,52,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla HuЙ—i Й“en, kala mo Alla HuЙ—i, a heЙ“aЕӢtaa mo ballo"
  4,53,"Kaa woodamЙ“e geЙ“al immorde e laamu ? Ountuma, Й“e okkataano yimЙ“e Й“en yeru hufol tamaro"
  4,54,"Kaa Й“e aГұay yimЙ“e Й“en e ko Alla Okki Й“e kon e ЖҒural Makko ? GomЙ—ii Men Okkii Й“eynguure Ibraahiima nden Deftere e Faltaare, Men Okki Й“e Laamu Mawngu"
  4,55,"Hino e maЙ“Й“e on gomЙ—inЙ—o nde, no e maЙ“Й“e kadi on faddiiЙ—o nde. Jahannama yonii huЙ“Й“aynge"
  4,56,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, aray Men Naada Й“e yiite : tuma kala guri maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“enndi, Men WaЙ—titana Й“e guri goo fii no Й“e meeЙ—ira lepte Й—en. Pellet, Alla Laatike FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,57,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, aray Men Naada Й“e Aljannaaji Й—i no ila e ley majji canЙ—i, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ndeer ton poomaa hino woodani Й“e ton rewЙ“e laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Men Naada Й“e Й—owdi duumiindi. @Corrected"